{"Id":19,"TicketNumber":"TKT-0019","Summary":"Implement Ontology skill group (v1, schema-only)","Description":"Create SKILLS/Ontology/ bundle with three skills: Ontology-Namespace-Define (configure base IRI and prefix mappings), Ontology-Build-Schema (introspect an XBase schema via XBase-Schema-TableList + XBase-Schema-ColumnList and generate an in-session OWL ontology document with owl:Class per table and owl:DatatypeProperty/owl:ObjectProperty per column), and Ontology-Export-Serialize (serialize the OntologyDocument to Turtle, JSON-LD, RDF-XML, or N-Triples). Register all three files in SKILLS.projitems, update CLAUDE.md and wiki docs. Scope: schema-only for v1 (no record population).","StatusId":5,"PriorityId":2,"CategoryId":null,"ReporterUserId":1,"AssignedToUserId":1,"ClosedAt":"2026-06-28T21:10:00Z","CreatedAt":"2026-06-28T21:00:00Z","UpdatedAt":"2026-06-28T21:10:00Z","IsDeleted":0,"IsArchived":0}
